CIPHER.0.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.0.cipherString: I think hell's a real place where real people spend a real eternity.

CIPHER.1.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.1.cipherString: He who lives in harmony with himself lives in harmony with the world.

CIPHER.2.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.2.cipherString: I'm so good and so loving that men don't believe it.

CIPHER.3.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.3.cipherString: The idea is to do out-of-the-box films that showcase my versatility and talent.

CIPHER.4.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.4.cipherString: Choose a job you love, and you will never have to work a day in your life.

CIPHER.5.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.5.cipherString: I try to only eat animals that are vegan. I'm probably the opposite of a vegan.

CIPHER.6.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.6.cipherString: We may have all come on different ships, but we're in the same boat now.

CIPHER.7.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.7.cipherString: The rare case where the conquered is very satisfied with the conqueror.

CIPHER.8.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.8.cipherString: With the new day comes new strength and new thoughts.

CIPHER.9.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.9.cipherString: I paint objects as I think them, not as I see them.

CIPHER.10.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.10.cipherString: When a marriage works, nothing on earth can take its place.

CIPHER.11.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.11.cipherString: Never have a companion that casts you in the shade.

CIPHER.12.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.12.cipherString: I don't really study the guys that I'm racing against.

CIPHER.13.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.13.cipherString: A toothache will cost a battle, a drizzle cancel an insurrection.

CIPHER.14.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.14.cipherString: No more war! Never again war! If you wish to be brothers, drop your weapons.

CIPHER.15.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.15.cipherString: Nothing is more hopeless than a scheme of merriment.

CIPHER.16.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.16.cipherString: The smallest deed is better than the grandest intention.

CIPHER.17.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.17.cipherString: If you have nothing to hide, there is no reason not to be transparent.

CIPHER.18.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.18.cipherString: Laughter is the sun that drives winter from the human face.

CIPHER.19.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.19.cipherString: I use Graf Edmonton for boots and John Wilson blades.

CIPHER.20.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.20.cipherString: The United States has been a global power since late in the 19th century.

CIPHER.21.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.21.cipherString: I have started that which the country will not willingly let die.

CIPHER.22.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.22.cipherString: I'd always listened to my parents' Bee Gees albums.

CIPHER.23.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.23.cipherString: The most efficient water power in the world - women's tears.

CIPHER.24.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.24.cipherString: The President is the CEO of this business that we call America.

CIPHER.25.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.25.cipherString: Bravery is being the only one who knows you're afraid.

CIPHER.26.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.26.cipherString: An inability to stay quiet is one of the conspicuous failings of mankind.

CIPHER.27.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.27.cipherString: Enjoyment is an incredible energizer to the human spirit.

CIPHER.28.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.28.cipherString: My parents are opposites who balance each other out.

CIPHER.29.question: K3 Aristocrat
CIPHER.29.cipherString: Never envy a man his lady. Behind it all lays a living hell.
